name: The Veggies "Black Hole Fun Cont."
description:
In collaboration with Rarebreeds and Atlanticfisherman.
After falling throught the black hole and into the lake, Carl and Beani went through a spring cave that led into the ocean. The mysterious events that followed had led them on a clash in their, apparent, hunt for this treasure chest; both utilizing their skills to summon friends to fight by their sides.
